{"tid":760012,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"傳說中的兔仔島：大久野島","createTime":"2018-07-29T07:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T02:36:10.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05fe4cee7beeb2e92fa5b714cfc91df44d138727","tid":760012,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家有沒有去過「兔兔島」大久野島？是兔迷必去的地方！有1000多隻自由自在地兔子活在這裡。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLF7jueXt6oU&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=367f60ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但是其實島內的兔仔有很多活得不開心和不長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predatory animals)的威脅，但是牠們很多有生病的、沒有足夠糧食及營養。所以兔迷下次去最好帶牧草, 例如: Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等等，給牠們最基本的糧食，高纖維。不要給高糖份的和零食。當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。以下video 可看到大久野島兔仔憂愁的時候:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d1cb506c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a> <br />\n<br />\n另一個video 看到兔子憂愁, 耳朵越後就越不開心。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ed17de5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a> <br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）很不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來 。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更多關於兔子憂愁的身體語言：<a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9baa9b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a></span>"},{"pid":"5e2353aa4d0316dd4a4bcd12a4ddab3a7de3e28c","tid":760012,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f05bdf793c43c30795f517f2d9756468213af93","tid":760012,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同ex去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aaa95e662b7fd0d54c789ed009c8dba3f3c18e4","tid":760012,"uid":67692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05fe4cee7beeb2e92fa5b714cfc91df44d138727","tid":760012,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家有沒有去過「兔兔島」大久野島？是兔迷必去的地方！有1000多隻自由自在地兔子活在這裡。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLF7jueXt6oU&d=NOp1Vkza2C8DAO0UI1TKxPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=367f60ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU</a><b